LineNo: 10881575,

Narrator: I walked down the palm-tree-lined p...
en


I walked down the palm-tree-lined path that connected Palas Rezna to the nearby House of Delegates.

LineNo: 10881677,

Narrator: In contrast to the ornate palace, t...
en


In contrast to the ornate palace, the House was essentially a plain concrete box. Its stripped-down appearance reflected its hurried construction.

LineNo: 10881779,

Narrator: The only adornment was a phrase chi...
en


The only adornment was a phrase chiseled above the entrance: "Ax Populat Rizati".

LineNo: 10881881,

Narrator: To the Rizian People.
en


"To the Rizian People".

LineNo: 10881983,

Narrator: I made my way down the hall to the...
en


I made my way down the hall to the meeting room.

LineNo: 10882085,

Narrator: Hugo rose to greet me as I entered...
en


Hugo rose to greet me as I entered the empty chamber. We took our seats atop the raised wooden platform in the center of the room.

LineNo: 10882187,

Narrator: Directly below the platform were tw...
en


Directly below the platform were two podiums, one for each speaker. Wooden benches for the delegates were arranged in a circle around us.

LineNo: 10882289,

Hugo Toras: Welcome, Your Majesty.
en


"Welcome, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 10882407,

Player_Romus: How are you, Hugo?
en


"How are you, Hugo?"

LineNo: 10882509,

Player_Romus: Good morning, Your Grace.
en


"Good morning, Your Grace."

LineNo: 10882611,

Narrator: The clock struck ten and the delega...
en


The clock struck ten and the delegates filed in.

LineNo: 10882713,

Narrator: Each wore a satin sash in the tradi...
en


Each wore a satin sash in the traditional color of his or her province: red for Rizia Imperii, blue for Monqiz, yellow for Cardesse-Montaklar and green for Brenas.

LineNo: 10882815,

Narrator: Next came the speakers. House Leade...
en


Next came the speakers. House Leader Daria de Rava walked out in a well-tailored crimson suit.

LineNo: 10882917,

Player_Romus: You said she's a loyalist.
en


"You said she's a loyalist."

LineNo: 10883019,

Player_Romus: Which house does she belong to aga...
en


"Which house does she belong to again?"

LineNo: 10883121,

Hugo Toras: Quite right.
en


"Quite right."

LineNo: 10883223,

Hugo Toras: The de Ravas aren't related to any...
en


"The de Ravas aren't related to any of the royal houses. They were granted their nobility status through service to our family after the War of Succession."

LineNo: 10883325,

Player_Romus: Remind me, how did she land this j...
en


"Remind me, how did she land this job?"

LineNo: 10883427,

Hugo Toras: Technically, she's a Baroness. But...
en


"Technically, she's a Baroness. But she prefers the title of Madam Speaker."

LineNo: 10883529,

Hugo Toras: She performed superbly as the head...
en


"She performed superbly as the head of the provincial council in Rizia Imperii."

LineNo: 10883631,

Narrator: I noted the approving tone in his v...
en


I noted the approving tone in his voice as he spoke of her.

LineNo: 10883733,

Narrator: Next came Manus Sazon, clad in a bl...
en


Next came Manus Sazon, clad in a black suit with a forest-green silk tie. He waved to his fellow delegates, then to me.

LineNo: 10883843,

Player_Romus_Italic: I returned his wave. He smiled as h...
en


I returned his wave. He smiled as he took his place.

LineNo: 10883849,

Player_Romus_Italic: I returned his wave. He smiled as h...
Menu Text en


Wave back to him.

LineNo: 10883951,

Player_Romus_Italic: I didn't move as he took his place.
en


I didn't move as he took his place.

LineNo: 10883957,

Player_Romus_Italic: I didn't move as he took his place.
Menu Text en


Don't wave.

LineNo: 10884059,

Narrator: Daria picked up a golden bell and r...
en


Daria picked up a golden bell and rang it once.

LineNo: 10884161,

Daria de Rava: Ladies and gentlemen, it is my pri...
en


"Ladies and gentlemen, it is my privilege to call this meeting of the House of Delegates to order."

LineNo: 10884263,

Daria de Rava: Today we are humbled by the presen...
en


"Today we are humbled by the presence of His Majesty King Romus, long may he reign."

LineNo: 10884365,

Narrator: A few cries of Long may he reign!...
en


A few cries of "Long may he reign!" echoed among the delegates, particularly those in red and blue sashes.

LineNo: 10884491,

Daria de Rava: The Rizian People's Party has prep...
en


"The Rizian People's Party has prepared a proposal that Mr. Sazon will submit before the Delegates and His Majesty."

LineNo: 10884593,

Daria de Rava: Mr. Sazon, would you like to expla...
en


"Mr. Sazon, would you like to explain more?"

LineNo: 10884695,

Manus Sazon: Gladly, Madam Speaker.
en


"Gladly, Madam Speaker."

LineNo: 10884797,

Manus Sazon: The past two decades have seen a m...
en


"The past two decades have seen a marked increase in workplace accidents, particularly in the sectors of mining and manufacturing."

LineNo: 10884899,

Manus Sazon: Now a cross-industry coalition of...
en


"Now a cross-industry coalition of employees has bravely approached the Rizian People's Party with a list of requests to convey to our fellow delegates as well as His Majesty."

LineNo: 10885001,

Manus Sazon: Among these are mandatory workplac...
en


"Among these are mandatory workplace safety training, upgraded protective equipment, benefits for those injured on the job, and regular site inspections by state authorities."

LineNo: 10885103,

Manus Sazon: Madam Speaker, Your Majesty, surel...
en


"Madam Speaker, Your Majesty, surely you agree on the urgency of this proposition. Rizia's great industries will not flourish as long as our workers are suffering."

LineNo: 10885205,

Narrator: I looked at Hugo.
en


I looked at Hugo.

LineNo: 10885323,

Player_Romus: It is an honor to be here, Madam S...
en


"It is an honor to be here, Madam Speaker."

LineNo: 10885425,

Player_Romus: Say that louder.
en


"Say that louder."

LineNo: 10885527,

Player_Romus: I am here to serve you, esteemed d...
en


"I am here to serve you, esteemed delegates. I look forward to your recommendations."

LineNo: 10885629,

Player_Romus_Italic: I let her continue.
en


I let her continue.

LineNo: 10885635,

Player_Romus_Italic: I let her continue.
Menu Text en


Don't say anything.

LineNo: 10885737,

Narrator: The hall reverberated with full-thr...
en


The hall reverberated with full-throated cries of "LONG MAY HE REIGN!" Daria smiled and continued.

LineNo: 10885839,

Narrator: She smiled and continued.
en


She smiled and continued.

LineNo: 10885941,

Daria de Rava: The Delegates will vote on whether...
en


"The Delegates will vote on whether to accept or reject it, but this is a non-binding recommendation. The ultimate authority rests with the King and the Royal Council."

LineNo: 10886043,

Player_Romus: So Rusty was right. His miners fou...
en


"So Rusty was right. His miners found a way to take their grievances to me."

LineNo: 10886145,

Player_Romus: How does he expect us to pay for a...
en


"How does he expect us to pay for all this?"

LineNo: 10886247,

Player_Romus: It's hard to believe we had none o...
en


"It's hard to believe we had none of these measures in place before now."

LineNo: 10886349,

Hugo Toras: Mr. Montoro will be expecting you...
en


"Mr. Montoro will be expecting you to make good on your promise to him."

LineNo: 10886451,

Hugo Toras: This is why I never brought these...
en


"This is why I never brought these meetings to your attention before. The proposals are impractical at best and ruinous at worst."

LineNo: 10886553,

Hugo Toras: And yet our industries flourished...
en


"And yet our industries flourished nonetheless."

LineNo: 10886655,

Narrator: I suddenly realized the hall had go...
en


I suddenly realized the hall had gone quiet.

LineNo: 10886757,

Manus Sazon: Shall I continue?
en


"Shall I continue?"

LineNo: 10886875,

Player_Romus: Please go on. I didn't mean to int...
en


"Please go on. I didn't mean to interrupt."

LineNo: 10886977,

Player_Romus: I've heard enough. I'd like to kno...
en


"I've heard enough. I'd like to know what Ms. de Rava thinks about the Worker Protections Act."

LineNo: 10887079,

Daria de Rava: Thank you, Your Majesty.
en


"Thank you, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 10887181,

Daria de Rava: Of course my party believes that w...
en


"Of course my party believes that worker safety is paramount. But the regulations that have been suggested today amount to overkill."

LineNo: 10887283,

Daria de Rava: It is up to individual corporation...
en


"It is up to individual corporations to take responsibility for reducing accidents. Shifting that responsibility to the government will do nothing to protect those at risk."

LineNo: 10887385,

Daria de Rava: It will, however, stifle our count...
en


"It will, however, stifle our country's economic growth and decrease our viability in the global arena."

LineNo: 10887487,

Daria de Rava: My point stands. With tensions ris...
en


"My point stands. With tensions rising in both our north and south, we simply cannot afford an extravagance of the type Mr. Sazon is proposing."

LineNo: 10887589,

Narrator: From near the front door came the s...
en


From near the front door came the sound of a single person applauding.

LineNo: 10887691,

Daria de Rava: My point stands. Rizia's gold and...
en


"My point stands. Rizia's gold and gas income is far from guaranteed at this moment."

LineNo: 10887793,

Hugo Toras: Busy as usual, Your Majesty.
en


"Busy as usual, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 10887895,

Hugo Toras: The delegates will be on their bes...
en


"The delegates will be on their best behavior with you here today."

LineNo: 10887997,

Narrator: She had a brisk gait and impeccable...
en


She had a brisk gait and impeccable posture. The other delegates practically held their breath as they waited for her to take her place.

LineNo: 10888115,

Hugo Toras: In all of the sessions I've attend...
en


"In all of the sessions I've attended, she has never made a decision that didn't align with the interests of House Toras."

LineNo: 10888217,

Hugo Toras: It's now her third term as speaker...
en


"It's now her third term as speaker. I do not believe she intends to vacate the position."

LineNo: 10888319,

Narrator: She flipped open a binder.
en


She flipped open a binder.

LineNo: 10888421,

Daria de Rava: Today's session is regarding the R...
en


"Today's session is regarding the Rizian Worker Protections Act."

LineNo: 10888801,

Hugo Toras: You're under no obligation to Mr....
en


"You're under no obligation to Mr. Montoro. But I would consider the costs of this proposal before saying yes to it."

LineNo: 10888903,

Player_Romus: Mr. Sazon, I would like to know ho...
en


"Mr. Sazon, I would like to know how Rizia is to pay for these policies."

LineNo: 10889005,

Narrator: He smiled patiently.
en


He smiled patiently.

LineNo: 10889385,

Manus Sazon: The Aureus gas field is expected t...
en


"The Aureus gas field is expected to generate considerable revenue once Rizian drilling operations begin. I see no harm in running a slight deficit until then."

LineNo: 10889765,

Manus Sazon: After all, in the end, this is a s...
en


"After all, in the end, this is a small price to pay for improving thousands of lives."

LineNo: 10889867,

Manus Sazon: Assuming the upcoming arbitrations...
en


"Assuming the upcoming arbitrations go our way, the Aureus gas field is expected to generate considerable revenue for Rizia."

LineNo: 10890247,

Manus Sazon: And in the end, this is a small pr...
en


"And in the end, this is a small price to pay for improving thousands of lives."

LineNo: 10890349,

Narrator: Manus cleared his throat.
en


Manus cleared his throat.

LineNo: 10890451,

Manus Sazon: As a wise man once said, 'A societ...
en


"As a wise man once said, 'A society is only truly prosperous if every one of its members is able to share in its wealth.'"

LineNo: 10890831,

Manus Sazon: As I was saying, my party and I be...
en


"As I was saying, my party and I believe that healthier workers will lead to a more prosperous society."

LineNo: 10890933,

Manus Sazon: What we invest in these measures n...
en


"What we invest in these measures now will pay off tenfold in the long run."

LineNo: 10891035,

Manus Sazon: What we invest in these measures n...
en


"What we invest in these measures now will pay off tenfold in the long run."

LineNo: 10891137,

Narrator: Manus stepped back from his podium,...
en


Manus stepped back from his podium, trying to conceal his disappointment. Daria eagerly approached hers.

LineNo: 10891517,

Daria de Rava: Our focus should be on achieving b...
en


"Our focus should be on achieving better diplomatic outcomes with our neighbors, not meddling in the affairs of our corporations."

LineNo: 10891619,

Manus Sazon: I must object, Madam Speaker. Comp...
en


"I must object, Madam Speaker. Companies such as Rizian Royal Gold and Rizian Oil and Gas will never voluntarily undertake the measures we're describing."

LineNo: 10891721,

Narrator: Daria brushed off the comment.
en


Daria brushed off the comment.

LineNo: 10892101,

Daria de Rava: Our focus should be on bolstering...
en


"Our focus should be on bolstering our economy, not meddling in the affairs of our corporations."

LineNo: 10892203,

Daria de Rava: My point stands. We should not be...
en


"My point stands. We should not be spending our wealth from the Aureus gas field acquisition before we have even earned it."

LineNo: 10892305,

Narrator: Daria sharply knocked on her podium...
en


Daria sharply knocked on her podium. All eyes turned to her.

LineNo: 10892407,

Daria de Rava: Forgive me, Your Majesty, but I ca...
en


"Forgive me, Your Majesty, but I cannot let my opponent continue with these lies."

LineNo: 10892509,

Narrator: Manus reluctantly took a step back.
en


Manus reluctantly took a step back.

LineNo: 10892611,

Manus Sazon: Our country still has a budget sur...
en


"Our country still has a budget surplus, Your Majesty. One that will only increase once drilling on the Aureus gas field begins."

LineNo: 10892991,

Manus Sazon: Our country still has a budget sur...
en


"Our country still has a budget surplus, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 10893093,

Manus Sazon: What is that wealth for, if not to...
en


"What is that wealth for, if not to improve the lives of our citizens?"

LineNo: 10893195,

Manus Sazon: Besides, a healthy worker is a pro...
en


"Besides, a healthy worker is a productive worker. This small investment will pay off tenfold in the long term. For us and for our economy."

LineNo: 10893297,

Narrator: I looked towards the source. Rusty...
en


I looked towards the source. Rusty was leaning against the wall, dressed in his usual plaid. He nodded at me as he kept clapping.

LineNo: 10893399,

Narrator: I turned towards Hugo again.
en


I turned towards Hugo again.

LineNo: 10893517,

Player_Romus: Who let him in?
en


"Who let him in?"

LineNo: 10893619,

Player_Romus: You didn't tell me that a special...
en


"You didn't tell me that a special guest would be joining us today."

LineNo: 10893721,

Player_Romus: Look, your favorite person's here.
en


"Look, your favorite person's here."

LineNo: 10893823,

Narrator: Hugo stared in Rusty's direction, e...
en


Hugo stared in Rusty's direction, expressionless.

LineNo: 10893925,

Narrator: Hugo stared in Rusty's direction, e...
en


Hugo stared in Rusty's direction, expressionless.

LineNo: 10894027,

Hugo Toras: I was not informed.
en


"I was not informed."

LineNo: 10894129,

Narrator: Hugo stared in Rusty's direction, e...
en


Hugo stared in Rusty's direction, expressionless.

LineNo: 10894231,

Hugo Toras: Unfortunately, these sessions are...
en


"Unfortunately, these sessions are open to the public."

LineNo: 10894333,

Hugo Toras: Unfortunately, these sessions are...
en


"Unfortunately, these sessions are open to the public. So we cannot ask him to leave without reason."

LineNo: 10894435,

Hugo Toras: We cannot ask him to leave without...
en


"We cannot ask him to leave without reason."

LineNo: 10894537,

Hugo Toras: I should have known he'd make an a...
en


"I should have known he'd make an appearance."

LineNo: 10894639,

Hugo Toras: In fact, his presence could be use...
en


"In fact, his presence could be useful in pressuring the Sazon boy to stand down with his demands."

LineNo: 10894741,

Narrator: Rusty had stopped clapping now. He...
en


Rusty had stopped clapping now. He was scrutinizing me closely, a gleam in his eye.

LineNo: 10894843,

Daria de Rava: How nice of you to join us, Mr. Mo...
en


"How nice of you to join us, Mr. Montoro. Do you have any words on the topic at hand?"

LineNo: 10894945,

Russello Montoro: Name's Rusty. And as a matter of f...
en


"Name's Rusty. And as a matter of fact, I do."

LineNo: 10895047,

Russello Montoro: Now, I won't take up too much of y...
en


"Now, I won't take up too much of your time. The Baroness summed things up pretty well."

LineNo: 10895149,

Russello Montoro: His Majesty here has also had the...
en


"His Majesty here has also had the privilege of hearing my personal thoughts on the subject."

LineNo: 10895251,

Narrator: Rusty ambled down the aisle of the...
en


Rusty ambled down the aisle of the chamber. He came to a stop between the two speaker podiums.

LineNo: 10895353,

Player_Romus: I side with the delegate majority....
en


"I side with the delegate majority. The workplace safety proposal from the Rizian People's Party shall not be undertaken."

LineNo: 10895455,

Player_Romus: I overrule the recommendation. The...
en


"I overrule the recommendation. The safety measures suggested by the RPP will be implemented in all industries with no exceptions."

LineNo: 10895461,

Player_Romus: I overrule the recommendation. The...
Menu Text en


"I overrule the recommendation. The safety measures suggested by the RPP will be implemented in all industries with no exceptions." [-2 Budget, -1 Budget Per Turn]

LineNo: 10895563,

Player_Romus: After listening to compelling argu...
en


"After listening to compelling arguments from both Mr. Sazon and Mr. Montoro, I hereby order the implementation of the RPP's proposal, with the addendum that the mining industry will be exempt from the new regulations."

LineNo: 10895569,

Player_Romus: After listening to compelling argu...
Menu Text en


"After listening to compelling arguments from both Mr. Sazon and Mr. Montoro, I hereby order the implementation of the RPP's proposal, with the addendum that the mining industry will be exempt from the new regulations." [-1 Budget]

LineNo: 10895671,

Russello Montoro: Damn straight, Your Majesty!
en


"Damn straight, Your Majesty!"

LineNo: 10895773,

Hugo Toras: Silence, Mr. Montoro. Do not make...
en


"Silence, Mr. Montoro. Do not make His Majesty regret his decision."

LineNo: 10895875,

Manus Sazon: The experts I've consulted with ha...
en


"The experts I've consulted with have pinpointed several factors responsible for the rise, chief among them a shortage of skilled labor and growing pressure from our primary trading partner."

LineNo: 10895977,

Manus Sazon: Simply put, our corporations have...
en


"Simply put, our corporations have been cutting corners, at the expense of human health and safety."

LineNo: 10896079,

Manus Sazon: His Majesty's decree to grant full...
en


"His Majesty's decree to grant full working permissions to guest workers has helped with the labor shortage, but these employees have been promoted in a rush, making conditions yet more hazardous."

LineNo: 10896459,

Manus Sazon: And of course, financial penalties...
en


"And of course, financial penalties for corporations that fail to meet these requirements."

LineNo: 10896561,

Daria de Rava: If our businesses are to remain co...
en


"If our businesses are to remain competitive, it is wiser to incentivize good safety practices than to punish their absence."

LineNo: 10896663,

Narrator: My uncle gave Rusty a withering loo...
en


My uncle gave Rusty a withering look.

LineNo: 10897043,

Russello Montoro: Son of a she-dog!
en


"Son of a she-dog!"

LineNo: 10897145,

Narrator: My uncle gave Rusty a withering loo...
en


My uncle gave Rusty a withering look.

LineNo: 10897247,

Hugo Toras: His Majesty has made his decision....
en


"His Majesty has made his decision. Do not question it."

LineNo: 10897349,

Narrator: Rusty glared at me, but said nothin...
en


Rusty glared at me, but said nothing.

LineNo: 10897643,

Russello Montoro: All hail the king!
en


"All hail the king!"

LineNo: 10897745,

Hugo Toras: Silence, Mr. Montoro. Do not make...
en


"Silence, Mr. Montoro. Do not make His Majesty regret his decision."

LineNo: 10897847,

Narrator: My uncle gave Rusty a withering loo...
en


My uncle gave Rusty a withering look.

LineNo: 10897949,

Player_Romus: What can we expect today?
en


"What can we expect today?"

LineNo: 10898051,

Hugo Toras: The usual.
en


"The usual."

LineNo: 10898153,

Hugo Toras: The Sazon boy will try to pass his...
en


"The Sazon boy will try to pass his latest impractical proposition, and the delegates will sensibly shoot it down."

LineNo: 10898271,

Hugo Toras: The silence from Wehlen has me rat...
en


"The silence from Wehlen has me rather on edge."

LineNo: 10898397,

Hugo Toras: The Pales naval standoff has me ra...
en


"The Pales naval standoff has me rather on edge."

LineNo: 10898793,

Player_Romus: Good that I'm here. It's about tim...
en


"Good that I'm here. It's about time someone listened to that kid."

LineNo: 10898895,

Player_Romus: Sounds like a waste of time.
en


"Sounds like a waste of time."

LineNo: 10898997,

Hugo Toras: No. And you shouldn't be, either.
en


"No. And you shouldn't be, either."

LineNo: 10899099,

Hugo Toras: There's a reason the King doesn't...
en


"There's a reason the King doesn't traditionally attend these sessions."

LineNo: 10899201,

Player_Romus: Impractical? I'll be the judge of...
en


"Impractical? I'll be the judge of that."

LineNo: 10899303,

Hugo Toras: I assure you that you'll agree wit...
en


"I assure you that you'll agree with me once the arguments are presented."

LineNo: 10899405,

Hugo Toras: The Sazon boy might even keep his...
en


"The Sazon boy might even keep his speeches to under a half hour."

LineNo: 10899523,

Player_Romus: Joke all you want, but it's about...
en


"Joke all you want, but it's about time someone listened to that kid."

LineNo: 10899625,

Player_Romus: Based on what I saw in Sallabes, I...
en


"Based on what I saw in Sallabes, I doubt it."

LineNo: 10899727,

Player_Romus: You're not jealous of the attentio...
en


"You're not jealous of the attention he gets, are you?"

Hugo Toras: Someone besides your daughter, you...
en


"Someone besides your daughter, you mean?"

Hugo Toras: Ha. Far from it. Although I am wor...
en


"Ha. Far from it. Although I am worried about the attention he's been getting from one Vina Toras."

LineNo: 10900033,

Hugo Toras: His speech there seemed to have do...
en


"His speech there seemed to have done a number on your daughter."

LineNo: 10900135,

Player_Romus: It's not a standoff. Just insuranc...
en


"It's not a standoff. Just insurance in case things go south at the AN."

LineNo: 10900237,

Player_Romus: Trust me, I'll be glad when it's o...
en


"Trust me, I'll be glad when it's over."

Player_Romus: Relax. Lucita has everything under...
en


"Relax. Lucita has everything under control."

en


"Duchess Azaro is 'Lucita' now?"

en


Hugo frowned pensively.

Hugo Toras: Will your war councilor, I wonder?
en


"Will your war councilor, I wonder?"

Hugo Toras: I trust Duchess Azaro is capable o...

"I trust Duchess Azaro is capable of de-escalation if necessary."

Player_Romus: Me, too. I hope your son's gambit...
en


"Me, too. I hope your son's gambit worked."

Player_Romus: President Smolak will be at the ne...
en


"President Smolak will be at the next AN session. We can corner him there if we need to."

Player_Romus: Nothing we can do about it now. Le...
en


"Nothing we can do about it now. Let's focus on today's meeting."

en


"I hope the investigators haven't found anything damning."

Hugo Toras: Madam Speaker, let the record show...

"Madam Speaker, let the record show that the King has aligned with the House majority."

"Madam Speaker, let the record show that the King has overridden the House majority."

en


"Noted, Your Grace."

Daria made a note in her binder, then looked up at Hugo and myself. If she was bothered by my decision, her face didn't show it.

Daria de Rava: Once again, I thank His Majesty fo...
